    - onHover: () => void (optional) — Mouse enter handler for hover state.
    - isDisabled: boolean (optional) — Disables the button when true.
    - isLoading: boolean (optional) — Shows a loading spinner when true.
    - children: React.ReactNode (optional) — Content to be displayed inside the button.
